title: KSHMR - Megalodon (Original Mix)
description:
KSHMR presents Megalodon on Spinnin' Records. Download on Beatport NOW : btprt.dj/1dobFNc

Ever since it appeared as an ID track in DJ sets and radio shows by the likes of Hardwell, Sander van Doorn, Nicky Romero, hype, rumors and speculations surround this track. Who produced it, what's the title, where did it come from? After it was featured in the teaser video for this years Spinnin' Sessions event in Miami, even more discussion followed. With the creator announced as KSHMR, the mystery continues. But evidentily the track speaks for itself. Make way for 'Megalodon'!
